quran[21{c,v,t}:
26,207,to woh samanِ zeist jo un ko mila howa hai inn ke kis kaam aeye ga ?
26,208,( dekho ) hum ne kabhi kisi bastii ko iss ke baghair halaak nahi kya ke uss ke liye khabardaar karne walay haq nasiyaat ada karne ko mojood thay
26,209,aur hum zalim nah thay
26,210,iss ( kitaab Mubin ) ko shyatin le kar nahi utre hain
26,211,"nah yeh kaam un ko sajta hai, aur nah woh aisa kar hi satke hain"
26,212,woh to is ki samaat taq se door rakhay gay hain
26,213,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, Allah ke sath kisi doosray mabood ko nah poukaro, warna tum bhi saza panay walon mein shaamil ho jao ge"
26,214,apne qareeb tareen rishta daaron ko dra-o
26,215,aur imaan laane walon mein se jo log tumhari pairwi ikhtiyar karen un ke sath tawaza se paish aao
26,216,lekin agar woh tumhari nafarmani karen to un se kaho ke jo kuch tum karte ho is se mein buri alz Meh hon
26,217,aur uss zabardast aur Raheem par tawakkal karo
26,218,jo tumhe is waqt dekh raha hota hai jab tum uthte ho
26,219,aur sajda guzaar logon mein tumhari naqal o harkat par nigah rakhta hai
26,220,woh sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
26,221,"logo, kya mein tumhe batau ke shyatin kis par utra karte hain ?"
26,222,woh har ja-al saaz badkaar par utra karte hain
26,223,"suni sunai baatein kaanon mein phonkay hain, aur un mein se aksar jhutay hotay hain"
26,224,"rahay shouraa, to un ke peechay behke hue log chala karte hain"
26,225,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke woh har waadi mein bhataktay hain
26,226,aur aisi baatein kehte hain jo karte nahi
26,227,"bajuz unn logon ke jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad kya aur jab un par zulm kya gaya to sirf badla le liya, aur zulm karne walon ko anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga ke woh kis injaam se dochar hotay hain"
